---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="세무회계본 | 강남 수서 세무사 - 상속·증여·양도 전문"
  description="강남 수서역 세무회계본. 14년 경력 천아름 대표세무사의 상속세, 증여세, 양도소득세 전문 컨설팅. 수서역 3번 출구 직결."
  canonical="https://taxbon.com/"
  currentPage="home"
>

<!-- 2. 메인 히어로 슬라이드 (자동/수동) -->
    <section id="home" class="relative h-[650px] bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden pt-20">
        <!-- 슬라이드 1: 천아름 대표 -->
        <div class="hero-slide active">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <img src="/images/사무실전경.jpg" alt="세무회계본 전경" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900/95 via-navy-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-full flex items-center">
                <div class="max-w-2xl text-white pt-10">
                    <div class="inline-block border border-gold-500 text-gold-500 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-6 tracking-wide">
                        천아름 세무사
                    </div>
                    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
                        상속·증여·양도,<br>
                        <span class="text-gold-500">가치를 지키는 솔루션</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        14년차 조세 전문가가 고객님의 소중한 자산을 지켜드립니다.<br>
                        복잡한 재산세제, 세무회계본이 가장 확실한 해답입니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4 flex-wrap">
                        <a href="#contact" class="bg-gold-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gold-600 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center">
                            상담 예약하기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="/intake" class="border-2 border-gold-400 text-gold-400 px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-gold-500 hover:text-white hover:border-gold-500 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center gap-2">
                            📋 준비서류 확인
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 슬라이드 2: 대형 법인 기장 자문 -->
        <div class="hero-slide">
            <div class="absolute inset-0">
                <img src="/images/20251211_163103.jpg" alt="비즈니스 미팅" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-navy-900/95 via-navy-900/70 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 h-full flex items-center">
                <div class="max-w-2xl text-white pt-10">
                    <div class="inline-block border border-green-400 text-green-400 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-bold mb-6 tracking-wide">
                        기장 자문 서비스
                    </div>
                    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
                        대형 세무법인 출신,<br>
                        <span class="text-green-400">모든 업종·규모 경험</span>
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        제조·요식·IT·부동산 법인까지 다양한 업종과 규모의 기장을 처리해왔습니다.<br>
                        고액자산 보유 법인의 지분 변동·세무조사 대응도 경험으로 답합니다.
                    </p>
                    <div class="flex gap-4">
                        <a href="https://booking.naver.com/booking/6/bizes/1181095" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="bg-green-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-green-700 transition shadow-lg inline-flex items-center">
                            기장 문의하기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="ml-2 w-4 h-4"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 슬라이드 변환 버튼 -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 flex space-x-3 z-20">
            <button class="hero-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gold-500 transition-all duration-300 ring-2 ring-transparent focus:ring-white"></button>
            <button class="hero-dot w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-gray-600 transition-all duration-300 ring-2 ring-transparent focus:ring-white"></button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 차별화된 서비스 -->
    <section id="why-taxbon" class="py-20 bg-gray-100">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <span class="text-gold-600 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Why Taxbon</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900 mt-2">왜 세무회계본(강남수서)일까요?</h2>
            </div>

            <!-- 외부 래퍼: 원형 가운데 + 4개 그리드 양옆 -->
            <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-8">

                <!-- 왼쪽 2개 카드 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full lg:w-2/5">

                    <!-- 카드 1: 원스톱 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition duration-200 flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="link" class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-800"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-bold text-sm mb-1.5">사업과 자산, 따로 보지 않습니다</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">기장부터 상속·증여·감정평가까지 한 곳에서. 사업과 자산을 함께 아는 곳에서 정확한 전략이 나옵니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 카드 2: 보안 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition duration-200 flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="shield-check" class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-800"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-bold text-sm mb-1.5">가족 자산 정보, 외부로 나가지 않습니다</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">사전예약제·내부 시스템·마스킹 처리·즉시 파쇄. 끝까지 책임집니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

                <!-- 가운데 원형: 검증된 실적 -->
                <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-52 h-52 rounded-full bg-navy-800 border-4 border-gold-500 flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center shadow-xl hover:scale-105 transition duration-300 cursor-pointer" onclick="window.location.href='/cases'">
                    <i data-lucide="file-check" class="w-8 h-8 text-gold-400 mb-2"></i>
                    <p class="text-white font-bold text-sm leading-snug mb-2">검증된 실적</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 text-xs px-4 leading-relaxed">말이 아닌<br>결과로 증명합니다</p>
                    <span class="mt-3 text-gold-400 text-xs font-bold flex items-center gap-1">
                        사례 보기 <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-3 h-3"></i>
                    </span>
                </div>

                <!-- 오른쪽 2개 카드 -->
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 w-full lg:w-2/5">

                    <!-- 카드 3: 합리적 가격 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition duration-200 flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="coins" class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-800"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-bold text-sm mb-1.5">합리적인 가격, 그대로 품질로</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">효율적인 운영으로 절감한 비용을 고급 세무 서비스 가격에 그대로 반영합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- 카드 4: 위치 -->
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-5 border border-gray-200 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md hover:-translate-y-0.5 transition duration-200 flex gap-4 items-start">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5 text-navy-800"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h3 class="text-navy-900 font-bold text-sm mb-1.5">여러 번 오가도 부담 없는 위치</h3>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs leading-relaxed">SRT·3호선·수인분당선·GTX-A 수서역 도보 5분. 주차 넉넉합니다.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3. 전문가 소개 (미니카드 선택 → 상세 패널) -->
    <section id="about" class="py-24 bg-white">
        <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <span class="text-gold-500 font-bold tracking-wider uppercase text-sm">Specialist</span>
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-800 mt-2">전문가 소개</h2>
                <p class="text-gray-500 mt-3 text-sm">전문가를 선택하면 상세 프로필을 확인하실 수 있습니다</p>
            </div>

            <!-- 미니 프로필 카드 4개 그리드 -->
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-8">

                <!-- 카드 1: 천아름 -->
                <button data-expert="0" id="expert-card-0"
                    class="expert-card text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-gold-400 focus:outline-none">
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 text-xl leading-tight mb-1">천아름</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gold-600 font-bold mb-3">세무사 · 대표</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">재산세제 및 부동산 세금 전문<br>상속·증여·양도소득세</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                        <span class="bg-navy-800 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#마을세무사</span>
                        <span class="bg-gold-500 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#대표</span>
                        <span class="bg-gold-100 text-gold-700 text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#14년경력</span>
                    </div>
                </button>

                <!-- 카드 2: 최지훈 -->
                <button data-expert="1" id="expert-card-1"
                    class="expert-card text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-amber-400 focus:outline-none">
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 text-xl leading-tight mb-1">최지훈</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-amber-600 font-bold mb-3">감정평가사 · 이사</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">부동산 감정평가 전문<br>기준시가·기타물건 자문</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                        <span class="bg-amber-600 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#감정평가사</span>
                        <span class="bg-amber-800 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#명문법인이사</span>
                    </div>
                </button>

                <!-- 카드 3: 김진범 -->
                <button data-expert="2" id="expert-card-2"
                    class="expert-card text-left p-6 rounded-2xl border-2 border-gray-200 bg-white shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-indigo-400 focus:outline-none">
                    <p class="font-extrabold text-gray-900 text-xl leading-tight mb-1">김진범</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-indigo-600 font-bold mb-3">공인회계사 · Partner</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">회계감사·기업가치평가<br>M&amp;A 및 투자자문</p>
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                        <span class="bg-indigo-600 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#공인회계사</span>
                        <span class="bg-indigo-800 text-white text-[11px] font-bold px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">#한서법인Partner</span>
                    </div>
                </button>
            </div>

            <!-- 상세 프로필 패널 -->
            <div id="expert-detail-wrapper" class="rounded-3xl overflow-hidden transition-all duration-300">

                <!-- 상세 0: 천아름 -->
                <div id="expert-detail-0" class="expert-detail flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]" style="display:none">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[220px] md:min-h-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                        <img src="/images/car.jpg" alt="천아름 대표세무사" class="w-full max-w-[180px] h-auto object-cover object-top rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                            <span class="bg-navy-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">#마을세무사</span>
                            <span class="bg-gold-500/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">#대표</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white relative">
                        <button class="expert-close-btn absolute top-4 right-4 w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors" aria-label="닫기">
                            <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </button>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">천아름 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">세무사</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-gold-500 font-bold mb-6">상속·증여·양도 / 재산세제 전문</p>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-gold-500"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>2011년 제48회 세무사 자격 취득</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>국립창원대학교 세무학과 졸업</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>前 세무법인 하나/동광 근무</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>前 세무법인 에이블 파트너</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gold-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>現 세무법인 성진(광주) 법인세 자문 / 회계법인 한서(종로) 세무 자문</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-navy-800 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span><strong class="text-navy-800 font-extrabold">2017년~현재 세무회계본 대표세무사</strong></li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>서울지방세무사회 감리위원 (2021.05~2023.05)</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>서울시 마을세무사 (2022.01~현재) 표창장4572호</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 상세 1: 최지훈 -->
                <div id="expert-detail-1" class="expert-detail flex-col md:flex-row min-h-[400px]" style="display:none">
                    <div class="w-full md:w-3/12 relative bg-gray-100 min-h-[220px] md:min-h-0 flex items-center justify-center p-4">
                        <img src="/images/KakaoTalk_20260205_143448097.jpg" alt="최지훈 감정평가사" class="w-full max-w-[180px] h-auto object-cover object-center rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                        <div class="absolute bottom-4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 flex gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap">
                            <span class="bg-amber-600/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">#감정평가사</span>
                            <span class="bg-amber-800/70 backdrop-blur-sm text-white px-2 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold">#이사</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="w-full md:w-9/12 p-8 md:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center bg-white relative">
                        <button class="expert-close-btn absolute top-4 right-4 w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-500 hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors" aria-label="닫기">
                            <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </button>
                        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">최지훈 <span class="text-lg text-gray-500 font-normal">감정평가사</span></h3>
                        <p class="text-amber-600 font-bold mb-6">부동산 감정평가 / 기준가격 자문</p>
                        <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
                            <h4 class="font-bold text-navy-800 mb-4 flex items-center text-base"><i data-lucide="award" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-amber-600"></i>주요 경력 및 이력</h4>
                            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed text-left">
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>2016년 감정평가사 자격 취득</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>고려대학교 화학과 졸업</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>前 중앙감정평가법인 본사 근무</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-gray-400 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>前 삼일감정평가법인 본사 근무</li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span><strong class="text-amber-700 font-extrabold">現 명문감정평가법인 본사 이사</strong></li>
                                <li class="flex items-start"><span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 mt-2 bg-amber-500 rounded-full mr-2 flex-shrink-0"></span>2025~2026년 지방세연구원 기타물건 기준가격 용역자문</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

